1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Science has a clearer story about transfer of learning than social media does.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:09,600
Transfer of learning means applying knowledge from one context to another.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:12,800
But did you know its effectiveness varies greatly?

4
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:17,600
Studies show it’s more effective when the similarities between contexts are clear.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:21,200
So, understanding how we learn can unlock our potential.

6
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:23,200
